// NOTE: attributes_after_line_change
//
// The cart attributes are updated AFTER the cart change is applied. This is to avoid
// a bug caused by other apps (e.g., Elevar) which try to update cart attributes after
// we update cart attributes. If another app tries to update cart attributes when we are
// changing line items, the line item change may not be applied (Shopify Ajax API limitation).
// By doing the cart attribute update second, we avoid this race condition.
//
// The ultimate solution would be to enable our global fetch queue to prevent race conditions,
// related to the setting `ajaxRaceConditionPrevention`. However, this is a risky change to
// make for all stores. Instead, we can use this workaround for now.

